# Reproducibility package: Public procurement in ICT (Compras.gov.br) â€” data and Python code

This repository contains the `.csv` datasets and the Python (Jupyter) notebook used to support the analyses of my academic paper on public ICT (Information and Communication Technology) contracts within Brazilian federal ministries, covering the 2020â€“2024 period.

> High-level objective: to diagnose and model procurement patterns and supplier characteristics in ICT contracts, supporting exploratory, inferential, and predictive analyses.

