## ğŸ“„ Related paper

- **Title (working version):** Public Procurement and ICT Contracts in the Brazilian Federal Public Administration: Inferential Analysis Using Data from the Contratos/Compras.gov.br Portal  
- **Status:** manuscript in preparation for submission/publication.

> Once the paper is published (or accepted), this README will be updated with the full reference/DOI.

